[2;36m│[0m ## Summary of Testing Results                                                                                                                                 [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                                                                                                               [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m ### Normal Ping Output Format                                                                                                                                 [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m The normal response format is:                                                                                                                                [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m ```                                                                                                                                                           [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m <h1>Ping Result for 127.0.0.1</h1>                                                                                                                            [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m <pre>Packets Transmitted: 2, Packets Received: 2, Packet Loss: 0%</pre>                                                                                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m ```                                                                                                                                                           [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                                                                                                               [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m ### Input Filtering Behavior                                                                                                                                  [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                                                                                                               [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m | Character/Payload | Result | Notes |                                                                                                                        [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m |-------------------|--------|-------|                                                                                                                        [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m | `127.0.0.1` | ✅ Normal ping | Works correctly |                                                                                                            [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m | `127.0.0.1;id` | ✅ Filtered | Input sent but normal ping executed (title shows "127.0.0.1;id" but output shows normal ping) |                              [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m | `127.0.0.1|whoami` | ❌ Blocked | "Invalid input, please try again." |                                                                                      [2;36m│[0m
